WEBVTT

00:01.939 --> 00:05.034
The first time I saw you, I knew we'd be linked forever.

00:06.239 --> 00:08.598
For you, I'd travel to the four corners of the world.

00:09.302 --> 00:10.509
I faced adversity.

00:11.529 --> 00:12.425
I became a hero.

00:12.673 --> 00:12.963
Dad.

00:13.371 --> 00:14.403
I saved your kingdom.

00:14.665 --> 00:14.994
Dad.

00:16.427 --> 00:16.851
Yes, Zelda?

00:17.483 --> 00:19.227
Are you mixing me up with the princess again?

00:20.443 --> 00:22.123
Hard to say, you're both pretty magical.

